asset.author: Dyson
asset.hookText: The Latest Gadgets dog comes face to face with the new Dyson Cinetic DC54 Animal. We unbox this new vacuum (with the "help" of the dog) and give it a quick test (at 1:45) on our cream carpet. The DC54 was very easy to assemble (no thanks to the dog at 1:22!) and performed very well as you can see from the test.
